# OpenHab

1. Arrancar OpenHab
- sudo systemctl start openhab.service

2. Crear una página de gráfica
	- Pages, + , Create Chart

Página Temperatura
ID: ComportamientoTemperatura
Label: Comportamiento Temperatura
Visible only to: Administrators, Users
Show on SideBar: On
Chart Type: Dynamic Period
Initial Period: h
- Add Grid
- Add Time Series, Configure Series
	- Name: Temperatura
	- Item: Canal Sensor temperatura
	
